h\n\nfunc (r *MetricsAggregatorReconciler) Reconcile(ctx context.Context, req ctrl.Request) (ctrl.Result, error) {\n\tlogger := log.FromContext(ctx)\n\tlogger.Info(\"Reconciling MetricsAggregator\", \"name\", req.Name, \"namespace\", req.Namespace)\n\treturn ctrl.Result{}, nil\n}\n\n// SetupWithManager sets up the controller with the Manager.\nfunc (r *MetricsAggregatorReconciler) SetupWithManager(mgr ctrl.Manager) error {\n\treturn ctrl.NewControllerManagedBy(mgr).\n\t\tFor(&multiarchv1beta1.ClusterPodPlacementConfig{}).\n\t\tComplete(r)\n}\n```\n\n### 2. Modified file: `cmd/main.go`\n\nHere are the exact changes to `cmd/main.go`:\n\n**Change 1 \u2014 Add import** (after the `\"github.com/openshift/multiarch-tuning-operator/internal/controller/podplacementconfig\"` import, line 70):\n\n```go\n\t\"github.com/openshift/multiarch-tuning-operator/internal/controller/podplacementconfig\"\n\t\"github.com/openshift/multiarch-tuning-operator/internal/controller/metricsaggregator\"\n```\n\n**Change 2 \u2014 Add the flag variable** (after `enableENoExecEventControllers bool` at line 94, add the new variable alongside):\n\nReplace:\n```go\n\tenableClusterPodPlacementConfigOperandWebHook,\n\tenableClusterPodPlacementConfigOperandControllers,\n\tenableENoExecEventControllers bool\n```\n\nWith:\n```go\n\tenableClusterPodPlacementConfigOperandWebHook,\n\tenableClusterPodPlacementConfigOperandControllers,\n\tenableENoExecEventControllers,\n\tenableMetricsAggregator bool\n```\n\n**Change 3 \u2014 Add leader election ID** (after the `enableENoExecEventControllers` leader ID block around line 130-135):\n\nAdd this block after the `enableENoExecEventControllers` block:\n```go\n\tif enableMetricsAggregator {\n\t\tleaderID = fmt.Sprintf(\"metrics-aggregator-%s\", leaderID)\n\t}\n```\n\n**Change 4 \u2014 Add the run call** (after the `enableENoExecEventControllers` run block, around line 199-201):\n\nAdd:\n```go\n\tif enableMetricsAggregator {\n\t\tRunMetricsAggregator(mgr)\n\t}\n```\n\n